      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so you won't find a single scratch or smudge anywhere. It drives like an absolute dream and is just waiting for someone who will love it as much as I have. If you're looking for perfection on wheels, this is definitely the one for you!",
