    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered legend. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features an 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies, delivering a linear power band and razor-sharp throttle response. Meticulously maintained, the double-VANOS system has been overhauled and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced\u2014essential for long-term chassis rigidity. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. The suspension remains taut with original bushings in excellent health, and the exterior retains its factory luster with zero signs of oxidation or clear coat failure. A true collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
